Kittinan Srithaworn is a Swiss Army knife at the lab. His expertise spans from frontend development, databases, to developing ML and NLP algorithms. He trained Deepcut, a deep learning model for Thai text tokenization. He also involves in multiple projects including Neuromatch Conference, DARPA Systematizing Confidence in Open Research and Evidence (SCORE), and Generating Thai Lyrics.

You can find more information on his GitHub: @kittinan.
